description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Staff Nurse – Catheter Laboratories (Cath Labs) (Registered &amp; Newly Qualified)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Working with us will provide you with an experience like no other to fast forward your career&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are a dynamic and enthusiastic team who assist with angioplasties, valvuloplasties, stent placements, implant pacemakers and implantable cardioverter- defibrillators (ICDs) as well as many other procedures.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Cardiology/Cath Labs department comprises of: 5 Angiography suites and a 6th hybrid suite, a Bronchoscopy suite. We provide essential care to our acute patients via our PPCI service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You might have just qualified, or be looking for a change or new challenge; you do not need to have previous Cath Lab or Bronchoscopy experience to join our team as we will provide comprehensive training. So if you are a dynamic, enthusiastic Nurse who wants to gain experience with us then come and join our highly motivated friendly team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What are we offering you?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A fantastic opportunity to learn new skills or to hone your Cardiothoracic skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learning from experts in the Cardiothoracic field with specialised training and support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dynamic and friendly working environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need the following attributes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;UK Registered Nurse&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enthusiasm and a willingness to learn&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills and organisational skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be highly motivated&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*There is a £1,000 welcome payment for all Band 5 posts upon starting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What our nurses say…..&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“Training and learning activities allow us to acquire a breadth of knowledge and skill”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“Supported in a highly motivated team who are friendly”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“I am able to develop my confidence through the competencies I achieve allowing me to establish a career as a Cath Lab nurse”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What our patients say…..&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“The staffs were exceptional, they left me well informed. All my appointments were on time or before, can’t speak highly enough of them”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“The staff were excellent throughout, kept me well informed of what was happening and what was going to happen”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“All the staff are friendly and welcoming”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Regular shortlisting takes place and you will be contacted for a Skype interview if you are shortlisted for interview.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*£1,000 welcome payment applicable to those who commence on substantive contracts with a commitment to remain with the Trust for a minimum of 12 months (excludes Bank contracts).&lt;/p&gt;
